# Aptitude Day 8 - Simple Interest and Compound Interest

Formulas

SI = (P × R × T)/100

Amount = P + SI

----------------------------------

CI

Amount = P(1 + R/100)^T

CI = Amount - P

----------------------------------

Example

P = 1000

R = 10%

T = 2

SI

= (1000 × 10 × 2)/100

= 200

Amount

= 1200

----------------------------------

CI

= 1000(1.1)^2

= 1210

CI

= 210

----------------------------------

